Title: Jack Reacher Official Trailer #1 (2012) - Tom Cruise Movie HD
Comment:
I read a comment somewhere where someone complained about the fact that many complain about Tom Cruise being to small to play Reacher. That someone thought that it was cool and refreshing that the hero was small, but still a tough hero.
But the thing is: Reacher from the novels is not a big hero in a small body. He is a very big guy. His fists are the size of grilled chickens. 
Tom Cruise does not compare when it comes to size. He is a very small guy. He is a good actor, who does very good in action movies. But it is very obvious that he read about Reacher, thought "Yeah! I wanna be (like) him!" and pulled some strings to get the novels made into movies, with him as the title character, even though he is the wrong size. Reminds me of this Norwegian who used a lot of resources on trying to get some old Norwegian novels in the cowboy genre made into movies with himself playing the hero. But the Norwegian did not have the same talent, money and power as Tom Cruise, so he failed...
